               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17540424-40-person339">
                  William 
                  Botter 
               <interp inst="t17540424-40-person339" type="surname" value="Botter"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540424-40-person339" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540424-40-person339" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On Tuesday was se'nnight coming with a child in my arms to the Old Jewry, after I had got through Aldgate two men followed and asked me if I had lost a handkerchief; I felt in my pocket, and said I had. They told me they had sent a man to take the person who had stole it, and the prisoner was brought to me presently after.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17540424-40-person340">
                  Joseph 
